@startuml
participant "仿真主循环" as Simulation
participant "供电服务" as Power
participant "车辆运行时管理器" as Vehicle
participant "供电网络模型" as Network
participant "FMU 物理引擎" as Fmu
participant "实时状态缓存" as Cache

Simulation -> Power: 准备外部供电拓扑()
activate Power
alt [供电拓扑未初始化]
  Power -> Network: POST /power-network/bootstrap
  activate Network
  Network --> Power: 拓扑初始化确认
  deactivate Network
else [已完成初始化]
  Power -> Network: GET /power-network/state
  activate Network
  Network --> Power: 供电网络状态快照
  deactivate Network
end
deactivate Power

Simulation -> Vehicle: 车辆运行时步进(运行标识，仿真步)
activate Vehicle
Vehicle -> Network: 查询当前供电约束(列车位置)
activate Network
Network --> Vehicle: 当前供电约束列表
deactivate Network
Vehicle -> Fmu: 批量物理步进
activate Fmu
Fmu --> Vehicle: 车辆物理输出列表
deactivate Fmu
Vehicle -> Network: 提交负荷与列车位置(运行标识，仿真步)
activate Network
Network --> Vehicle: 下一控制周期供电约束列表
deactivate Network
Vehicle --> Simulation: 列车状态列表和车辆物理输出列表
deactivate Vehicle

Simulation -> Power: 根据车辆输出更新供电状态()
activate Power
Power -> Network: GET /power-network/state
activate Network
Network --> Power: 供电网络状态快照
deactivate Network
Power -> Cache: 更新分区状态()并发布事件
deactivate Power
@enduml
